MySQL/SQL Injection Prevention
1. Use ORM with Parameterized Queries
Sequelize, like most ORMs, automatically parameterizes queries, providing protection against SQL injection: safe-mysql-resolvers.js

2. Avoid Raw Queries When Possible
If you must use raw queries, ensure you use parameterization: insecure_raw-query-mysql-resolvers.js


3. Input Validation and Sanitization: mysql-validation.js, then use these valiation function
